{"tid":1384930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"｛提議｝誠邀海外項目經理精英整理香城反送中項目工程文件","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:02:50.000Z","uid":270078,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7b6033dd8b4b18e49af711a827722927efcef379","tid":1384930,"uid":270078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:26:55.000Z","msg":"由於政府無能，香城市民被迫接左反送中的job, 但依項世紀工程普通市民無法持續跟進每個項目， 導致好多細項被放棄了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實到時又可以俾料同監察官方獨立調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實有冇精英已儲開同整理緊依個世紀工程的資料， 我想大家都可以幫忙， 重要project scope 包括:<br />\n政客賣港資料庫（當中包括中聯辦葉虎事件， 何議員與鄉黑關連）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警員犯例資料庫 (我知老豆搵仔有做都夠料，係難d 直接extract data）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於題材敏感， 不宜本地人士主導，想問其實家陣有冇人有相同想法或其實已經做緊，特別係外國巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16257ec7b1cd0cebdd3c2e249a5296f8443c0447","tid":1384930,"uid":270078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:33:02.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a2440d15f2dc4447f1bda475af6234029d6a0cc5","tid":1384930,"uid":270078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:40:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e5ef982545abfc61d7d9545dc490c5e8b672cd1e","tid":1384930,"uid":270078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:51:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"034308558b3fe3ee74c0c88ea1a9a2ebf44f4a3c","tid":1384930,"uid":270078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3991c451f26fa6855bea7afc9a143283c483ee1b","tid":1384930,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5b713e93ba183422dc4af4714a2121a52bb450","tid":1384930,"uid":270078,"like":0,"di